# VoxKage Environment Variables
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Add your API tokens below to enable VoxKage integrations.
# Use: voxkage plugins add <name>  to configure interactively.
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Telegram Bot Integration ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get your bot token from @BotFather on Telegram (/newbot command)
# TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=
# TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=

# ── Spotify Integration ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get credentials from https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard
# SPOTIFY_CLIENT_ID=
# SPOTIFY_CLIENT_SECRET=

# ── GitHub Integration ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Generate a PAT from https://github.com/settings/tokens
# GITHUB_PAT=

